Package com.nokia.maps.kml.component

The component package provides kml components to render KML map objects and interact with KML features in the JavaME Location API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    KMLEventListener
    This interface defines a callback method which is used when the currently focused KML object has changed.
    KMLMapComponent
    This interface defines a MapObject collection created from a KML file, and the wiring to display a highlighted MapObject and fire a callback to an object listening to this component.
    KMLResultSet
    This interface defines the processed data from a KML Document in the form of MapObjects and details of specified Features.
